<type>(<scope>): <subject>

# ── TYPES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# feat     A new feature added to the dashboard
# fix      A bug fix (include what broke and what file)
# docs     Documentation only (README, CHANGELOG, guides, PDFs)
# data     Database, CSV, or demo data changes
# refactor Code restructure — no new feature, no bug fix
# style    UI/visual changes only (colors, layout, labels)
# research Evidence review, research_log.json, RESEARCH_FOUNDATION.md
# chore    Config, requirements, GitHub Actions, tooling

# ── SCOPES (optional but recommended) ───────────────────────────────────────
# dashboard        dashboard.py changes
# command-center   coach_command_center.py
# athlete-profile  athlete_profile_tab.py
# forecast         Forecast tab
# insights         Insights tab (evidence review, correlations, ask)
# evidence         research_monitor.py, research_log.json
# models           train_models.py, models/
# data             generate_database.py, waims_demo.db
# docs             README, guides, PDFs
# deps             requirements.txt, .env

# ── EXAMPLES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# feat(command-center): Add positional readiness strip (Guards/Wings/Bigs)
# fix(dashboard): Resolve datetime comparison error in Tab 1 readiness sort
# docs(readme): Update tab count to 8, add model validation section
# research(evidence): Tighten PubMed queries — filter clinical noise
# style(command-center): Replace clinical load language with coach language
# refactor(models): Unify readiness formula across all tabs via pkl scorer
# data(database): Regenerate demo DB with GPS columns and availability table

# ── RULES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Subject line: 50 chars max, imperative mood ("Add" not "Added")
# No period at end of subject line
# Leave blank line between subject and body if adding detail
